            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR3a0014-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:34:10.986+09:00">文中子说:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:34:14.152+09:00">'‘圆形的物体易动，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:34:20.984+09:00">方形的物体易静,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-1a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:34:21.824+09:00">这体现了天地的本质呀!"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-2a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:34:45.366+09:00">文中子说:"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-2a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:34:52.348+09:00">睿智者快乐，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-2a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:34:56.851+09:00">是因为他心中可包容万物。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-2a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:35:07.988+09:00">仁爱者长寿，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-2a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:36:03.555+09:00">是因为他忘却自我私欲。"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-3a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:36:14.929+09:00">文中子说:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-3a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:36:19.221+09:00">''姚义，清素而端庄；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-3a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:36:23.566+09:00">李靖，惠物而勇断；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-3a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:36:27.951+09:00">窦威，和容而博识；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-3a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:36:31.629+09:00">薛收,体旷而志肃；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-3a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:37:01.369+09:00">贾琼,通明而果毅;杜淹,诚意而威厉;房玄龄，志精而用密；魏征，直道而遂行；温大雅，量深而宽宏；陈叔达,简静而中正。这些人如遇良机，官职不会低于卿相，然而礼乐方面却不完备。”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-11a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T18:17:36.744+09:00">文中子说:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-11a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T18:19:56.028+09:00">"文士中有缺衣少食还乐于'道'之人， 【靡（mǐ):无，没有。《诗经•大雅•荡》:“靡不有初,鲜克有终。"】</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-11a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T18:17:51.615+09:00">我还没有见过。”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-10a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T18:20:07.52+09:00">内史薛道衡在长安见到文中子，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-10a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T18:20:18.419+09:00">归来对其子薛收说:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-10a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T18:20:33.864+09:00">"《河图》、《洛书》</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-10a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T18:20:43.244+09:00">尽在王夫子那里，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-10a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T18:20:56.944+09:00">你前往以他为师，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-10a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T18:21:16.111+09:00">不会缺失此二方面的教育。”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-12a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T18:24:49.805+09:00">文中子对魏征说:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-12a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T18:25:06.702+09:00">"你和王凝都是天生直谏之人。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-12a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T18:25:27.297+09:00">魏征你，果行;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-12a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T18:25:33.728+09:00">王凝他，挺物。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-12a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T18:25:51.854+09:00">若可并行于时，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-12a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T18:26:52.103+09:00">皆为有用之才。"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-13a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T21:04:10.204+09:00">文中子对李靖说:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-13a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T21:04:15.156+09:00">"王凝他，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-13a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T21:04:26.195+09:00">若被君王重用，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-14a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T21:05:14.289+09:00">则王法不挠曲。"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-14a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T21:05:31.053+09:00">李靖问：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-14a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T21:05:44.588+09:00">'’用机智怎样?''</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-14a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T21:18:07.963+09:00">文中子说:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-14a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T21:18:20.289+09:00">"应把仁作为自己的责任，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-14a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T21:18:29.741+09:00">小人凭机智背弃仁义是贼，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-14a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T21:18:31.564+09:00">君子凭机智背弃仁义为作乱。”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-15a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T21:52:10.786+09:00">2.14 薛收问：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-15a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T21:20:08.033+09:00">“仲长子光是怎样的人？”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-15a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T21:20:20.67+09:00">先生说：“是天人。”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-15a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T21:20:26.881+09:00">薛收问：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-15a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T21:20:37.044+09:00">“什么是天人？”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-15a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T21:20:44.728+09:00">先生说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-15a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T21:20:53.114+09:00">“其形渺小，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-15a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T21:21:13.036+09:00">因此属于人；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-15a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T21:21:20.979+09:00">其道广大，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-15a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T21:24:10.704+09:00">因此独能成全他的天性。”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-16a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T21:53:24.937+09:00">2.15 贾琼问君子之道，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-16a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T21:53:34.445+09:00">先生说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-16a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T21:53:44.308+09:00">“首先一定是恕吧！”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-16a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T21:53:52.763+09:00">问：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-16a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T21:53:59.202+09:00">“敢问恕指的是什么？”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-16a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T21:54:11.616+09:00">先生说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-16a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T21:54:21.601+09:00">“做儿子的，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-16a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T21:54:44.573+09:00">体察他父亲的想法行事；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-16a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T21:54:51.124+09:00">做弟弟的，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-16a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T21:54:55.898+09:00">体察他兄长的想法行事。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-16a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T21:55:14.181+09:00">以此类推扩大到全天下，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-16a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T21:58:08.465+09:00">就可以了。”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-17a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T21:59:45.242+09:00">2.16 先生说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-17a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T21:59:53.949+09:00">“君子在道德上取得进益，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-17a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T22:00:12.289+09:00">小人在财货上取得进益。”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-18a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T23:34:21.585+09:00">楚公发难，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-18a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T23:34:50.587+09:00">派使臣召见文中子。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-18a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T23:35:02.654+09:00">文中子不去，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-18a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T23:35:32.451+09:00">"你替我感谢楚公，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-18a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T23:35:54.53+09:00">天下大乱，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-18a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T23:35:23.524+09:00">对使臣说:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-18a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T23:36:44.795+09:00">除非王公出自内心深处的诚意不能安生，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-18a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T23:37:10.048+09:00">并非无'道'</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-18a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T23:37:52.482+09:00">只是'祸'先行。"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-25a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-06T04:23:54.698+09:00">薛方士问入葬的原则。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-25a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-06T04:24:01.275+09:00">文中子说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-25a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-06T04:25:29.059+09:00">"贫穷的人仅以黄土埋尸身，  【敛:又作"殓”，收敛。分大敛、小敛。大敛，将死者放入棺中;小敛，给死者穿上寿衣。】</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-25a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-06T04:24:33.04+09:00">富贵的人有棺有椁。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-25a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-06T04:24:40.368+09:00">用作陵地的封域不要广阔。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-25a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-06T04:24:47.407+09:00">不要占据良田。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-25a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-06T04:24:51.424+09:00">古人不以死去的人伤害生存的人，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-25a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-06T04:25:11.289+09:00">不应以厚葬作为礼制。”</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
